Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.45,0:19:09.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙，想要時空轉移！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.17,0:19:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯，和侵入白星的艾因斯特一起！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.25,0:19:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.52,0:19:18.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一起去吧，溫德爾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.42,0:19:21.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到因果地平線的彼岸！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.09,0:19:26.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手啊！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.62,0:19:34.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉移坐標Z,0,9，最終指令，阿波羅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.41,0:19:40.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赫裏奧斯…！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.76,0:19:51.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.29,0:19:54.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉移力場麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.19,0:19:57.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基利亞姆…啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.26,0:20:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！？
